Description:
Windows 10 operating system for personal computers developed by Microsoft within Windows NT. 
After Windows 8 system got the number 10, bypassing 9. The system is designed to be the same 
for different devices such as personal computers, tablets, smartphones, Xbox One, etc. 
Available to a single development platform and single store universal app, compatible with 
all supported devices. Among the important innovations â€” the voice assistant cortana, 
the ability to create and switch multiple desktops etc.

Description: 
Microsoft Office 2016 good illustration of how today has changed the approach to document creation and 
collaboration with them. Many of us start working on one computer and continue it on another, 
and demonstrate on the third, simultaneously managing to make small changes at a laptop,
 tablet or even smartphone. Therefore, Office 2016 have tried to make it conceptually different. 
Virtually all of the key elements in it were designed from scratch, and apps are focused on a 
single style of work regardless of the hardware platform. They are designed to provide the usual 
functionality on any device, automatically adjusting its interface to the parameters 
of the current screen and the available system resources.
 

At the time of installation is recommended to disable antivirus solutions - 
the process will be much faster and the probability of successful activation will increase a lot.
